name: ROZLYTREK 100 MG
treatmentDescriptions: NTRK Gene Fusion-Positive Solid TumorsROZLYTREK is indicated for the treatment of adult and pediatric patients older than 1 month of age with solid tumors that:• have a neurotrophic tyrosine receptor kinase (NTRK) gene fusion without a known acquired resistance mutation,• are metastatic or where surgical resection is likely to result in severe morbidity,and• have either progressed following treatment or have no satisfactory alternative therapy.ROS1-Positive Non-Small Cell Lung CancerROZLYTREK is indicated for the treatment of adult patients with metastatic non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) whose tumors are ROS1-positive.
warnings: תרופה מוגבלת לרישום ע'י רופא מומחה או הגבלה אחרת
